name: Ingenious Discoverers
overview:
Ingenious Discoverers is a specialized recruiting firm with dedicated practice areas. At ID, we focus on excellence in all areas of our business with proven methodologies, excellent customer service and quality candidates. ID provides the flexibility and personal service, with the resources, experience and reach of a large global search firm.

ID specializes in providing all levels of professionals with domain expertise across specific industries and technical expertise across different platforms. We focus on Information Technology, IT Enabled Services, Telecom, Media and Entertainment, Engineering, Process and Infrastructure, Consumer Services and Retail, Banking, Financial Services and Insurance.
